description: Reings is bringing the heat – a fully equipped kitchen & restaurant on wheels. Serving-up a delicious array of “Traditional with a twist” eats such as burgers, tacos and wings. It does not stop there, their Chef can prepare any dish for your next catering event.  Come out and join them on the weekend at the Houston Premier Outlet Mall on 290 for great food and excellent customer service.
name: REIGNS
